Package ch.fhnw.ht.eit.p2.impedancepro

Class Summary
ComplexNumber The ComplexNumber class provides a simple way to use complex basic operations (e.g. multiplication of to complex values).
DocumentUtil The DocumentUtil class enables a simple way of loading files like PDF or similar.
ElectricalComponent An instance of the ElectricalComponent class represents an electrical component (e.g. a capacitor) with a value and a tolerance.
EngineeringUtil The EngineeringUtil class contains methods to handle engineering notation.
GraphPanel The GraphPanel class is able to show a JFreeChart by setting the dataset of the public XYPlot plot.
GraphView The GraphView holds the GraphPanel for the return loss plot.
ImageUtil The ImageUtil class provides a simple way of loading images.
ImpedancePro The ImpedancePro class contains the main method.
ImpedanceProController The ImpedanceProController class triggers the models calculations, as soon as there are changes in the view.
ImpedanceProModel  
ImpedanceProView The ImpedanceProView class is the main view of ImpedancePro.
InformationPanel A simple panel with a help and an info button
InputPanel Contains all inputs of a source or a load.
InputView The InputView combines two InputPanels.
JEngineeringTextField The JEngineeringTextField can read 'engineering notated' strings and only allows correct formated numbers.
JIntegerTextField The JIntegerTextField only allows correct formated integers.
MatchingNetwork Represents the matching network with all its electrical components.
MonteCarloPanel The MonteCarloPanel class contains all the inputs for the monte- carlo simulation.
Network Represents the whole network consisting of a source, a matching and a load network.
PropertiesView The PropertiesView combines a MonteCarloPanel and a ReturnLossPanel.
SettingsPanel The ReturnLossPanel class contains the settings for the graphs.
SolutionPanel The SolutionPanel displays the solution with an image and numerical values.
SolutionView The SolutionView class combines up to 4 SolutionPanels.
SourceLoadNetwork Represents either the source or the load network.
WebIncDecButton A simple increment / decrement button based on a WebButtonGroup of the WebLookAndFeel
